<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.7">
<l>vaṇṇan tirivum maṉaṅkuḻaivum māṉami lāmaiyum vāyveḷuppu</l>
<l>muṇṇa luṟāmaiyu muṉmelivu mōtanīr vaṇṇaṉeṉ pāṉoruvaṉ</l>
<l>taṇṇan tuḻāyeṉṉu mālaikoṇṭu cūṭṭat taṇiyum, pilampaṉṟaṉṉaip</l>
<l>paṇṇaḻi yappala tēvaṉveṉṟa pāṇṭi vaṭatteṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The change in [my] complexion, the languishing heart, the lack of modesty,</l>
<l rend="indent">the pallor of the lips,</l>
<l>the inability to eat, the inner suffering – [these] will be soothed when [I am] adorned</l>
<l rend="indent">with the garland known as the cool, pretty tulsi garland</l>
<l>of the man known as the ocean-hued [Lord]!</l>
<l>Send me to the banyan tree Pāṇṭi, where Baladeva defeated Pralamba</l>
<l rend="indent">So that [his] gait is destroyed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
